text: Aziz Court Imperial is a skyscraper in Chittagong, Bangladesh. It is Located in Agrabad, the central business district. It rises to a height of and has 32 floors. The construction of this building started in 2014 and was completed in 2017. It is the second tallest building in Chittagong and the fifth tallest in Bangladesh. ==See also== * List of tallest buildings in Bangladesh * List of tallest buildings in Chittagong ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Agrabad
title: Aziz Court Imperial
